The United States strongly condemns the terrorist attack by Hamas in the southern West Bank, in which four Israelis were killed. The US expresses condolences to the victims' families and urges that the terrorists responsible for the attack be brought to justice. The Palestinian Authority has also condemned the attack. The attack highlights the lengths to which those opposed to peace will go to obstruct progress. It is important for both parties to persevere and continue working towards a just and lasting peace that ensures security for all in the region.